stream
BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (HOW TO USE THIS PLANNER) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.0 Td (Hey there, beautiful brain.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.0 Td (This planner was made for people who've tried every budgeting app, spreadsheet, and) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.0 Td (envelope system... and abandoned them all by Day 3.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 634.2 Td (HERE ARE THE ONLY RULES:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 618.2 Td (- Done beats perfect. A half-filled page is better than a blank one.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 604.2 Td (- Use pencil. You'll change your mind. That's fine.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 590.2 Td (- Only 5 spending categories. Seriously. Five. Not fifteen.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 576.2 Td (- One line per day for tracking. That's it. One line.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 562.2 Td (- Skip pages you don't need. There's no planner police.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 548.2 Td (- Celebrate every tiny win. Paid a bill on time? CHAMPION.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 520.4 Td (WHAT'S INSIDE:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 504.4 Td (- Monthly Budget Overview ............ Pages 6-17) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 490.4 Td (- Weekly Spending Tracker ............ Pages 18-21) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 476.4 Td (- Bill Pay Command Center ............ Pages 22-23) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 462.4 Td (- Impulse Spending Tools ............. Pages 24-26) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 448.4 Td (- Savings & Debt Visual Trackers ..... Pages 27-30) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 434.4 Td (- Annual Overview & Reflection ....... Pages 31-35) Tj ET
endstream
